</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>而在网友晒出的照片，却是这副“鬼样子”：</p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201020/447a933b98f4456a99a7fd3704661ce4.png" /></p>
<p>像某宝上9.9包邮的劣质拖鞋；</p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201020/a7f915bcd2f54bfdbca2e00a9d32ea6b.png" /></p>
<p>路边的垃圾桶；</p>
